title: You don't have to be strong || EP:105
description:
Hey Rehabbers,
Today's title might catch you off guard a bit. I hope you truly listen to this episode and understand the truth behind the title. You're not weak because you decide to "quit", and you're not strong behind you decide to keep going. Being Mentally smart is more important than being mentally tough. Share this with someone you care about.
